[`BasesEntryGroup`](BasesEntryGroup)

## BasesEntryGroup class

A group of BasesEntry objects for a given value of the groupBy key. If there are entries in the results which do not have a value for the groupBy key, the key will be the [NullValue](NullValue)<!-- -->.

 1.10.0
